Description: Implements a highly optimized MCMC sampler for the Random Phase-Amplitude Gaussian Process (RPAGP) model, as described by Pluta et al. (2024) <doi:10.1038/s41598-024-59579-2>. Provides robust and fast inference on trial-level ERP data characteristics like amplitude and latency.
